{"id":18044,"date":"2024-01-06T18:56:18","date_gmt":"2021-01-06T13:26:18","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/?p=18044"},"modified":"2024-11-11T15:59:05","modified_gmt":"2024-11-11T10:29:05","slug":"wall-painting-ideas-for-bedroom","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/bedroom-interiors\/wall-painting-ideas-for-bedroom\/","title":{"rendered":"7 Creative Wall Painting Ideas For Your Bedroom"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p><em>Level up your space with these creative bedroom wall painting ideas<\/em><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>If it is difficult to leave the comfort of your bed every morning, a feeling we are all familiar with. It is even more difficult to create a cosy bedroom ambience that makes it hard for you to leave. Among the many factors that contribute to making a bedroom space feel like your zone of comfort, the colour of your walls are a vital design aspect. It is no secret that colours can prove to be soothing, comforting and a lot more.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>When you think of wall painting ideas for bedroom there are colours that instantly pop up as a part of your consideration. There doesn&#8217;t have to be a standard colour template for you to follow. You can experiment with colours for bedroom walls and trust us the effects unique colour combinations present can be stunning! Go through these seven creative wall painting ideas for your bedroom for some colour-inspiration.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Get a Free Modular Kitchen Worth \u20b92 Lakhs with Your Home Interiors.\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/08183703\/designcafe-offer-free-modular-kitchen-worth-2-lakhs.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Use A Fresh Colour For Highlighting<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p> While everyone loves basking in a bit of sunshine, too much of a bright shade of yellow can be overwhelming for your bedroom. The colour yellow works really well when combined with neutral colours and the combination of grey and yellow is a classic. It&#8217;s equally appealing when this combination is used to brighten up your bedroom space. Inbuilt shelving in this bedroom wall is a great way to add decor as well as design in one go. Keep the larger part of the wall grey and highlight the space with bright yellow as a refreshing addition. <\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/06171307\/yellow-wall-paint-design-idea-for-bedroom.jpg\" alt=\"Grey and yellow combination wall painting brightens the area, Wall painting idea for bedroom.\" class=\"wp-image-18053\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/06171307\/yellow-wall-paint-design-idea-for-bedroom.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/06171307\/yellow-wall-paint-design-idea-for-bedroom-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/06171307\/yellow-wall-paint-design-idea-for-bedroom-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/06171307\/yellow-wall-paint-design-idea-for-bedroom-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">A bright colour like yellow can effectively transform the look of your bedroom<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">50 Shades Of Teal<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Teal is a versatile colour and one that is commonly used with furnishing and decor. Muted tones of teal look amazing on bedroom walls, adding sophisticated undertones to <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/bedroom-interiors\/modern-bedroom-designs\/\">modern bedroom designs<\/a>. With a muted tone like this you have ample scope to play around with complimentary colours for the rest of the space.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/06171301\/shades-of-teal-paint-color-idea-for-bedroom-walls.jpg\" alt=\"Paint color idea for bedroom walls, Bedroom walls painted in shades of teal colour looks fantastic\" class=\"wp-image-18052\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/06171301\/shades-of-teal-paint-color-idea-for-bedroom-walls.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/06171301\/shades-of-teal-paint-color-idea-for-bedroom-walls-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/06171301\/shades-of-teal-paint-color-idea-for-bedroom-walls-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/06171301\/shades-of-teal-paint-color-idea-for-bedroom-walls-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Teal or its many variants make for great wall painting ideas for the bedroom<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Go All Out With Red<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>This colour is not for the weak-hearted! If you want to embrace your wild, passionate side then go all out with a red painted wall. The balancing element lies in the finish and texture of such wall colour. Paired with the right kind of decor the colour definitely seems like something that can be pulled off without your <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/interior-design\/bedroom-design\/\">bedroom design<\/a> seeming too loud for comfort.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/06171249\/red-wall-painting-idea-for-bedroom.jpg\" alt=\"Bedroom wall coloured in red with beautiful look, wall paint design idea for the bedroom.\" class=\"wp-image-18050\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/06171249\/red-wall-painting-idea-for-bedroom.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/06171249\/red-wall-painting-idea-for-bedroom-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/06171249\/red-wall-painting-idea-for-bedroom-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/06171249\/red-wall-painting-idea-for-bedroom-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Red is a bold and beautiful choice for bedroom wall paint colour<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">The Right Shade Of Yellow<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>While a bright shade of yellow for bedroom walls can seem like too much to take, the right shade of yellow is magical to say the least. The overall design and decor of this bedroom is full of warm with natural colours such as shades of brown that help tone down the effect of too much yellow in the bedroom. The use of white along with the right textures too helps make yellow one of the better options for wall painting ideas for bedroom.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/06171255\/shade-of-yellow-idea-for-wall-painting-bedroom.jpg\" alt=\"Wall paint color for bedroom idea, master bedroom walls in a shade of yellow coloured look bright\" class=\"wp-image-18051\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/06171255\/shade-of-yellow-idea-for-wall-painting-bedroom.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/06171255\/shade-of-yellow-idea-for-wall-painting-bedroom-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/06171255\/shade-of-yellow-idea-for-wall-painting-bedroom-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/06171255\/shade-of-yellow-idea-for-wall-painting-bedroom-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Yellow when paired with warm colours makes the bedroom seem bright and cosy<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Powder Blue As A Wall Painting Idea<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Who doesn&#8217;t love soothing colours? The understated powder blue colour for the walls of this bedroom add a sense of calm and peacefulness to space. The entire bedroom is dual toned, the warm colour of wood and the decor work in contrasting harmony with the softness of&nbsp;blue walls. You can opt for different pastel shades such as mint green, pastel pinks, and so on for soothing <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/bedroom-interiors\/bedroom-paint-colours\/\">bedroom paint colours<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/06171243\/powder-blue-interior-wall-painting-idea-for-bedroom.jpg\" alt=\"Calm and peaceful powder blue coloured bedroom wall is an easy wall painting idea for bedroom.\" class=\"wp-image-18049\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/06171243\/powder-blue-interior-wall-painting-idea-for-bedroom.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/06171243\/powder-blue-interior-wall-painting-idea-for-bedroom-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/06171243\/powder-blue-interior-wall-painting-idea-for-bedroom-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/06171243\/powder-blue-interior-wall-painting-idea-for-bedroom-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Pastels are powerful and it is a great idea to paint your walls in this palette<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Go Green With Wall Paint<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>This bedroom is proof that there is no such thing as too much green! The paint colours for green are in a dual tone, and the theme is carried forward most of the furniture and decor in the bedroom without making it seem overbearing. Going for neutral or natural colours for combination makes perfect sense so as to not topple the overall colour-balance of the space.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/06171237\/green-scale-wall-paint-colors-for-bedroom-ideas.jpg\" alt=\"Interior wall painting idea for the bedroom, dual-tone green coloured walls in bedroom look refreshing.\" class=\"wp-image-18048\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/06171237\/green-scale-wall-paint-colors-for-bedroom-ideas.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/06171237\/green-scale-wall-paint-colors-for-bedroom-ideas-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/06171237\/green-scale-wall-paint-colors-for-bedroom-ideas-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/06171237\/green-scale-wall-paint-colors-for-bedroom-ideas-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">The colour green has our heart when it comes to bedroom wall painting ideas<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Lets plan your home interiors together, speak to designers now\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/28124401\/lets-plan-home-interiors-together.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Wall Painting Ideas For Bedroom In the Colour Blue<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>If blue can be soothing, it can also be nice and bright! The royal shade of blue makes this bedroom space look fresh, energetic and fun! The brightness of the colour is balanced with the use of a darker and deeper shade of blue for the adjacent wall, while the decor is fresh, bright and minimal.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/06171232\/easy-wall-painting-idea-for-bedroom-with-blue.jpg\" alt=\"Bedroom wall coloured in a royal shade of blue look energetic, an idea for wall painting bedroom.\" class=\"wp-image-18047\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/06171232\/easy-wall-painting-idea-for-bedroom-with-blue.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/06171232\/easy-wall-painting-idea-for-bedroom-with-blue-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/06171232\/easy-wall-painting-idea-for-bedroom-with-blue-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/06171232\/easy-wall-painting-idea-for-bedroom-with-blue-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Blue walls can infuse brightness into the bedroom space<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>We bet you never considered some of these wall painting ideas for bedroom before. Which one of these are you planning to try out for your bedroom?<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Also, Check out<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/bedroom-interiors\/vastu-colours-for-bedroom\/\">Vastu Colours For Bedroom<\/a><\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-interiors\/simple-wall-painting-ideas\/\">Simple Wall Painting Ideas<\/a><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"row blog-form\">\n\t<div class=\"offset-lg-3 col-lg-6 bg-light\">\n<fiel